Name: Darkwaronline
About the game: Sci Fi RPG game the game was designed mainly as MMORPG where you drive your chosen robot, it can be manually or with the automated system ... As you level up you will get new skills and you can use new weapons and equipment ... Find items from 1 to 6 stars with 6 stars being the best items for the character's inventory Send the objects by mail to your other characters or if you are playing on a network send by mail using the names of those characters ... Eliminate the enemies reaches level 90 fill yourself with the best objects. Visual Basic 6.0
